====================================
Customer Scoring System
====================================

1. DEMOGRAPHICS (Max: 20 Points)
------------------------------------
- Age:
  - Teenagers (13-19 years): 1 Point
  - Young Adults (20-34 years): 2 Points
  - Middle-Aged Adults (35-54 years): 3 Points
  - Older Adults (55+ years): 4 Points
- Gender:
  - Male: 1 Point
  - Female: 1 Point
  - Non-Binary: 2 Points
  - Prefer Not to Say: 0 Points
- Location (Time Zone):
  - Eastern (ET): 2 Points
  - Central (CT): 2 Points
  - Mountain (MT): 1 Point
  - Pacific (PT): 1 Point
- Income Level:
  - Low (Under $35,000): 1 Point
  - Lower Middle ($35,000 - $74,999): 2 Points
  - Upper Middle ($75,000 - $149,999): 3 Points
  - High ($150,000+): 4 Points

------------------------------------

2. SHOPPING BEHAVIOR (Max: 15 Points)
------------------------------------
- Frequency of Shopping:
  - Frequent Shopper: 5 Points
  - Occasional Buyer: 3 Points
  - Sale-Only Shopper: 1 Point
- Channels Used:
  - Online: 3 Points
  - In-Store: 2 Points
  - Both: 5 Points
- Peak Shopping Times:
  - Weekdays: 2 Points
  - Weekends: 3 Points
  - Sale Events: 5 Points

------------------------------------

3. PURCHASE HISTORY (Max: 15 Points)
------------------------------------
- Types of Products Bought:
  - Electronics: 5 Points
  - Fashion: 3 Points
  - Groceries: 2 Points
  - Other: 1 Point
- Average Spend per Transaction:
  - Under $50: 1 Point
  - $50-$100: 2 Points
  - $100-$500: 3 Points
  - Over $500: 5 Points
- Brand Loyalty:
  - Yes: 5 Points
  - No: 0 Points

------------------------------------

4. ONLINE BEHAVIOR (Max: 10 Points)
------------------------------------
- Browsing Patterns:
  - High Engagement: 5 Points
  - Medium Engagement: 3 Points
  - Low Engagement: 1 Point
- Wishlist/Add-to-Cart Usage:
  - Frequently Adds Items: 5 Points
  - Occasionally Adds Items: 3 Points
  - Rarely Adds Items: 1 Point
- Social Media Influence:
  - Highly Influenced: 5 Points
  - Moderately Influenced: 3 Points
  - Not Influenced: 1 Point

------------------------------------

5. FEEDBACK AND REVIEWS (Max: 10 Points)
------------------------------------
- Provides Feedback:
  - Yes: 5 Points
  - No: 0 Points
- Tone of Reviews:
  - Positive: 5 Points
  - Neutral: 3 Points
  - Negative: 0 Points
- Constructive Feedback Provided:
  - Yes: 5 Points
  - No: 0 Points

------------------------------------

6. PROMOTION SENSITIVITY (Max: 10 Points)
------------------------------------
- Sensitivity to Discounts:
  - High: 5 Points
  - Medium: 3 Points
  - Low: 1 Point
- Participation in Sales:
  - Yes: 5 Points
  - No: 0 Points

------------------------------------

TOTAL SCORE: _________ / 80

Customer Type (Based on Score):
------------------------------------
- 0-20: Casual Shopper
- 21-40: Moderate Shopper
- 41-60: Engaged Shopper
- 61-80: VIP Shopper
